title: How to Make Blueberry and Pineapple Jello with Cream Cheese Topping

steps.headline: Add blueberries with juice and pineapple.
Beat cream cheese with sugar and vanilla until smooth.
Top with chopped nuts and chill until firm.

text: Dissolve Jello in water.  Add blueberries with juice and pineapple.  Pour into 9 x 13-inch dish.  Chill until firm.  Beat cream cheese with sugar and vanilla until smooth.  Spread over blueberry mixture.  Top with chopped nuts and chill until firm.  Enjoy! Yield: 12-14 servings. Finished.
